;;   www.google.com:
;;   ,----
;;   | (global-set-key (kbd "C-c m g")
;;   |                 (lambda ()
;;   |                   (interactive)
;;   |                   (firefox-controller-send-key-sequence
;;   |                    "C-t C-l www.google.com <return>")))
;;   `----

;;   Make sure your key sequence can be read by the `kbd' function.



